<h4 id="make">Make</h4>
<p>make主要用来构建c语言的项目，实际上，任何主要某个文件有变化，就要重新构建项目，都可以用make构建</p>

<h4 id="语法">语法</h4>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>target <span class="o">[</span>target...] : <span class="o">[</span>dependent ....]
    <span class="o">[</span><span class="nb">command</span> ...]
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="suffix">Suffix</h4>
<ol>
  <li>Make uses a special target, named <strong>.SUFFIXES</strong> to allow you to define your
own suffixed</li>
</ol>
